<LOAD BALANCER>
1. Copy this folder to /opt/
2. Add entries to /etc/hosts

   172.16.XXX.1    mgmt.tc.net   
   172.16.XXX.3    rdpa.tc.net
   172.16.XXX.4    rdpb.tc.net
   
3. Add this line to /etc/rc.local
   python /opt/lb_mgmt/lb_mgmt.py

<UPSTART>   
4. Copy the upstart script file 'upstart/lb_mgmt.conf' inside '/etc/init/'

5. Issue command 'initctl list' and see if lb_mgmt is on the list
    If status is 'stop/wating' issue command 'start lb_mgmt'
    Issue command 'status lb_mgmt' and the process 'lb_mgmt' should be running

<LOGROTATE>
6. Copy the file 'logrotate.d/lb_mgmt' into '/etc/logrotate.d/'
